data.description: Charming one-level home in Santa Clara on a large corner lot with RV parking! This is a one owner home that was purchased new by the seller and features vaulted ceilings a cozy fireplace as well as a large master bedroom with walk in closet and private bath. Low maintenance landscaping with an underground sprinkler system.
